    (f n r x) * Complex.exp (-2 * Real.pi * Complex.I * (h.val * x.val : ℕ) / (q n : ℂ))

/--
Definition of the physical variance sigmaSq.
Define the physical variance of the survivor distribution as:
  $$ \sigma^2 = \frac{1}{q}
       \sum_{x=0}^{q-1} (f(x) - \mu)^2 $$
-/
